text: Upper Hunter is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 1856, abolished in 1856, recreated in 1904, reabolished in 1920 and recreated again in 1927. It is a conservative electorate and has only ever been held by conservative parties as an electorate with one member. It is currently held by Dave Layzell of the National Party. ==Election results== The swings above have been calculated from the 2021 Upper Hunter state by-election. ==References== Upper Hunter
